resources No(40)
notes
Tristatic UHF observations (Beata) of ionospheric conditions during HF-Heating
reproducing specles of enhanced optical emissions in diffuse/pulsating aurora,
and ionospheric modification of auroral arcs. A requirement for running this
experiment is previous substorm activity. This experiment is a collaboration
between KTH Stockholm (N Ivchenko), IRF Kiruna (T Sergienko) and UIT Tromso (B
Gustavsson)
